        <prompt>What was the primary economic impact of the Panic of 1873 on Reconstruction?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Reduced Northern support for Reconstruction programs</option>
            <option letter="b">Increased federal spending in the South</option>
            <option letter="c">Improved Southern industrial growth</option>
